readable.content: A big black dog chases a big brown dog with a green object in his mouth while another big brown dog tags behind . A brown dog holds an object in its mouth while a black dog tries to take it away . Another brown dog looks on . Three dogs fight for a green chew toy on a stone walkway . Three dogs running together on a paved walkway . Two dogs chase a third dog with a toy .
